    <item>
      <title>英国财政部长里夫斯审查终止私募股权税收减免的办法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/uk-s-reeves-reviews-approach-to-closing-private-equity-tax-break</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，英国财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 仍打算取消私募股权的税收减免，但正在重新审视其方法，以最大限度地增加税收收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/uk-s-reeves-reviews-approach-to-closing-private-equity-tax-break</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2024 12:52:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院任期开始之际，特朗普的竞选之路充满变数</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/supreme-court-returns-to-ghost-guns-trans-care-and-maybe-trump-cases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院在总统选举的阴影下开始新一届任期，这可能会给已经深陷国家政治分歧的最高法院带来新的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/supreme-court-returns-to-ghost-guns-trans-care-and-maybe-trump-cases</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>《泰晤士报》称工党考虑改变私募股权税上调政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/labour-weighs-u-turn-on-private-equity-tax-increase-times-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《泰晤士报》援引未具名人士的话称，英国工党政府正考虑改变对私募股权投资者增税的计划，此前有警告称，这项措施最终的成本将超过其收益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/labour-weighs-u-turn-on-private-equity-tax-increase-times-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2024 11:48:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列袭击黎巴嫩，袭击贝鲁特郊区和北部</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-10-05/israel-strikes-lebanon-hitting-beirut-suburbs-and-the-north</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列特拉维夫（美联社）——以色列周六扩大了对黎巴嫩的轰炸，对贝鲁特南部郊区进行了 12 次空袭，并首次袭击了黎巴嫩北部腹地的一个巴勒斯坦难民营。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-10-05/israel-strikes-lebanon-hitting-beirut-suburbs-and-the-north</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2024 11:44:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将重返巴特勒遇刺现场以支持竞选活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/trump-goes-back-to-butler-assassination-site-to-bolster-campaign</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普将重返七月刺杀事件发生地，公开处理此次袭击事件的后果，此次袭击弄伤了他的耳朵并颠覆了竞选活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/trump-goes-back-to-butler-assassination-site-to-bolster-campaign</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥地利极右翼抨击“邪恶”的冻结计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/austrian-election-winning-far-right-derides-plan-to-freeze-it-out</link>
      <description><![CDATA[奥地利极右翼领导人赫伯特·基克尔 (Herbert Kickl) 加大言论力度，使得他的自由党受到众多选民的欢迎，但却疏远了他组建联合政府所需的政治对手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/austrian-election-winning-far-right-derides-plan-to-freeze-it-out</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2024 10:20:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>圣保罗市长竞选考验博索纳罗对巴西右翼的掌控力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/sao-paulo-mayor-race-tests-bolsonaro-s-grip-on-the-brazilian-right</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在周日的市政选举之前，一位叛乱候选人正在分裂巴西的右翼，考验着雅伊尔·博索纳罗对狂热运动的控制力，即使在两年前失去总统职位后，他仍然试图领导这场运动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/sao-paulo-mayor-race-tests-bolsonaro-s-grip-on-the-brazilian-right</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡政治礼品丑闻中被指控的亿万富翁：问答</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/the-billionaire-charged-in-singapore-s-political-gift-scandal-q-a</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这是新加坡自上世纪 80 年代以来最严重的部长级不当行为调查，调查对象是一位亿万富翁，他因将一级方程式赛车引入新加坡而闻名，而且他与政治的关系可以追溯到几十年前。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/the-billionaire-charged-in-singapore-s-political-gift-scandal-q-a</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2024 08:29:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度外交部长将于 2015 年以来首次访问巴基斯坦</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/india-foreign-minister-to-visit-pakistan-for-first-time-since-2015</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度政府周五晚间表示，外交部长苏布拉马尼亚姆·杰尚卡尔 (Subrahmanyam Jaishankar) 将代替总理纳伦德拉·莫迪 (Narendra Modi) 出席在巴基斯坦举行的中国主导的峰会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-05/india-foreign-minister-to-visit-pakistan-for-first-time-since-2015</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 05 Oct 2024 06:21:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟发起新一轮电动汽车关税战，考验中国勇气</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/eu-tests-its-mettle-to-take-on-china-with-new-ev-tariff-fight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟对中国动用了其最有力的经济工具之一，对电动汽车征收关税，此举增加了中国采取报复措施以及对国内消费者和企业产生不利影响的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/eu-tests-its-mettle-to-take-on-china-with-new-ev-tariff-fight</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 15:33:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
